However, there is an alternate point of entry
along the building's side, just on top of this ledge.

353
00:19:55,156 --> 00:19:59,325
The terrain doesn't permit easy access,
so security, while present, isn't as strong.

354
00:20:01,614 --> 00:20:03,892
You don't want the madman to have his way, do you?

355
00:20:04,435 --> 00:20:05,537
Courage, children!

356
00:20:06,639 --> 00:20:08,110
